      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Rumors that you’ve become a proper leatherworker have reached even the back alleys of #m10003000#. Got me curious whether they're actually true. From the looks of it, you’ve built up some skill and experience… but are you really better than me? Let’s see what you’ve got."
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Tch, pretty confident, aren’t you? Fine. Then go take down #r#o22#s#k near #m10003000#, and bring me #b1 #t3010005##k. I’ll be waiting. Heh…"
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Looks like you haven’t reached that level yet. And you expect me to call you my partner like this?"
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Let’s take a look… Huh. This isn’t bad at all. Tch—fine, I’ll admit it. This is solid work. I’m honestly surprised you’ve built up this much skill. Yeah, this is good enough to call you a real leatherworker. Alright, you’ve earned my respect. Guess I should give you something special…"
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "This #t4130000# is a special item that can change the stats of equipment when used during crafting. It’s pretty unstable, so sometimes the results can be disappointing—but if you handle it right, you might end up with something beyond your expectations."
        },
        "1": {
          "_dirName": "1",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "If you really want to test the limits of your leatherworking skills, I’d say give it a try. Heh… and don’t get lazy with your training."
        }
      },
